<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="width-n">width <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /wɪdθ/    美 /wɪdθ/  </p>
<p>[U] &amp; [C] [常与 a 连用]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>宽度；幅度：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a <strong>width of</strong> four feet / four feet <strong>in width</strong>
4英尺宽</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a road of great width 
很宽阔的马路</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>What’s the width of the Thames at London? 
泰晤士河在伦敦地区的宽度是多少?</p></div></div>